Program: Omnibus
Title: The Kogi
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p0376k10
Last Broadcast Date: 19 March 1991
Talking about a rare visit to The Kobi tribe in Colombia who call themselves 'the elder brothers of humanity'. The programme looked at their history and culture which has existed since pre-columbian era and listened to their warning about the future of the earth.